data.title: Front Row Tickets for Jonas Brothers Remember This Tour
meta_keywords: front row tickets for jonas brothers in camden
jonas brothers announce remember this tour
data.meta_description: The Jonas Brothers just announced their 'Remember This Tour', and SoJO 104.9 and Republic Records want you to stare right into their eyes from the FRONT ROW!
data.text:
The Jonas Brothers just announced their 'Remember This Tour', bringing them to our South Jersey this October! SoJO 104.9 and Republic Records want you to stare right into their eyes from the FRONT ROW!

It's 'Only Human' to want to be as close to Kevin, Joe and Nick as possible when they hit BB&T Pavilion along Camden Waterfront on October 7th. And, SoJO's got the goods: FRONT ROW SEATS.

Tickets for the Jonas Brothers 'Remember This Tour' go on sale soon Monday, May 27th and SoJO 104.9 has plenty of tickets to give away! Plus, one lucky winner will be upgraded to SoJO VIP status with two FRONT ROW TICKETS!

We'll have lots of different ways for you to win your Jonas Brothers tickets and qualify for those front row seats, just make sure you have the SoJO 104.9 app downloaded with all notifications turned on (including 'contests') so you receive our Jo Bros. alerts!

Jonas Brothers are also dropping new music this week with Marshmellow we can't wait for you to hear.

**Must be 18 to win. Grand Prize winner will be drawn at random on on Thursday, May 27, 2021.

SOURCES: LiveNation.com
